Please specify the reason why the employee was not entitled to public holiday pay:

Premium pay is 1.5 times an employee's regular rate of pay. If an employee is entitled to receive premium pay for work on a public holiday, they must be paid 1.5 times their regular rate of pay for each hour worked on the public holiday.
Did the employee receive, or will the employee receive, a substitute day for this public holiday?
